      "line": 61,
      "text": ".NE FACTOR DETERMINES all else"
    },
    {
      "line": 62,
      "text": "about our relationship with our chil-"
    },
    {
      "line": 63,
      "text": "dren: it is irreversible. The contract"
    },
    {
      "line": 65,
      "text": "ee cannot be broken. Daily we leave"
    },
    {
      "line": 66,
      "text": "jobs, none friends, lovers, but the child always"
    },
    {
      "line": 67,
      "text": "comes along."
    },
    {
      "line": 70,
      "text": "When the going is rough - when we don’t like"
    },
    {
      "line": 71,
      "text": "each other - my son and I can’t call it quits and"
    },
    {
      "line": 72,
      "text": "cut our losses. I can’t pack a bag, make a break"
    },
    {
      "line": 73,
      "text": "for it, perhaps find a more compatible child. Were"
    },
    {
      "line": 74,
      "text": "it even the remotest of possibilities, everything else"
    },
    {
      "line": 75,
      "text": "; would change."
    },
    {
      "line": 78,
      "text": "So I take risks with him I"
    },
    {
      "line": 79,
      "text": "would never dare take with"
    },
    {
      "line": 80,
      "text": "anyone else. I treat him badly,"
    },
    {
      "line": 81,
      "text": "with rough impatience, with"
    },
    {
      "line": 82,
      "text": "all the bile I hide from friends"
    },
    {
      "line": 83,
      "text": "and lovers for fear of losing"
    },
    {
      "line": 84,
      "text": "them. I am less tolerant of"
    },
    {
      "line": 85,
      "text": "deviation and idiosyncrasies"
    },
    {
      "line": 86,
      "text": "with him. We fight - bitterly"
    },
    {
      "line": 87,
      "text": "- then, sad and weary of it,"
    },
    {
      "line": 88,
      "text": "make up with a tentative kiss."
    },
    {
      "line": 89,
      "text": "I demand so much: love,"
